snippet.title: Apple II Classics - Threshold
snippet.description:
This series is a personal journey into the past, reexperiencing the Apple II games I played during my formative years.

Some useful Apple II links:
http://kegs.sourceforge.net/
http://apple2online.com/
http://www.virtualapple.org/

Series playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLBk6-z6v3pDL8cDTcfn1V6ZGULl502DXF
